net.akaish.kitty.orm.annotations.column.constraints

Annotation Type DEFAULT


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Inherited
public @interface DEFAULT
    Annotation for column constraint DEFAULT.
    Configurator would parse this annotation in following order:
    Fetching expression(), if not set (default value) than next step, otherwise creating DEFAULT constraint with this expression.
    Fetching literalValue(), if not set (default value) than next step, otherwise creating DEFAULT constraint with this value.
    Fetching predefinedLiteralValue(), if not set (default value) than next step, otherwise using one of predefined literals such as TRUE or CURRENT_DATE defined in LiteralValues.
    Fetching signedInteger(), if not set than would be created DEFAULT constraint with value 0 (DEFAULT 0) Created by akaish on 30.04.2018.
